## Risks and Mitigations

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-------------|--------|------------|
| Context window overflow | Medium | High | Token budget allocation, chunked context |
| Prompt injection via file content | Low | High | Sanitize injected context, review @-mentions |
| Model version drift | Medium | Medium | Pin model version in Cursor settings if available |
| Inconsistent output between sessions | Medium | Medium | Maximize explicit constraints, minimize ambiguity |

